            "Risk Factor": "Newborn",
            "Likely Organism": "MRSA,MSSA,GBS,Gram Negative",
            "Initial Empiric Antibiotic Therapy'": "Vancomycin15mg/kg load, then reduce dose, ANDceftazidime30mg/kg IV q12 h"
          },
          {
            "Risk Factor": "Children",
            "Likely Organism": "MRSA,MSSA",
